icrosoft is making massive investments in both Azure and in its products ar=
ound AI that it doesn=E2=80=99t control, and the best alternative to not ow=
ning the AI undergirding both is to hedge its bets by increasing the number=
 of suppliers. The important thing =E2=80=94 which was revealed during that=
 episode =E2=80=94 is that Microsoft has leverage because it owns GPUs. Fro=
m an Update ( https://stratechery.com/2023/sam-altman-back-at-openai-q-goin=
