What this does re-emphasize is that Microsoft, for all of the criticism the=
y arguably deserve for basing the company=E2=80=99s technical future on a p=
artner with such an inherently unstable structure, ultimately held the trum=
p cards because of its combination of compute capacity and access to OpenAI=
 IP; =E2=80=9Che who controls the GPUs controls the universe=E2=80=9D, at l=
east for now, which is why Microsoft got what they wanted: Altman as CEO an=
d OpenAI=E2=80=99s employees back at work.

Microsoft=E2=80=99s products are still being built around OpenAI, to be cle=
ar; the short-term outcome of this agreement is that Mistral will be availa=
ble to developers as a part of Azure=E2=80=99s Models-as-a-Service. Buildin=
g that out, though, also moves Microsoft down the road to switching over, s=
hould the need some day arise.

This also, I should note, calls into question the idea that Mistral is goin=
g to be a European champion to rival the American tech companies. Foundatio=
n models matter hugely, but it=E2=80=99s not clear that they are going to b=
e a sustainable point of differentiation; right now what matters is having =
GPUs, which by-and-large means the contenders are Microsoft, Google, and Am=
azon.

To that end, I think it is notable that Amazon didn=E2=80=99t make a deal w=
ith Mistral first; on one hand, this does seem like a miss, given that Amaz=
on doesn=E2=80=99t own a widely-used foundational model. On the other hand,=
 Amazon=E2=80=99s play is to serve everyone, and its own managed service, B=
edrock, just announced it is adding Mistral ( https://www.aboutamazon.com/n=
ews/aws/mistral-ai-amazon-bedrock ). Why invest if you are going to get the=
 model regardless? Microsoft has a more pressing need for some degree of co=
ntrol, however small, because it is using AI in its core products, in addit=
ion to Azure; that need is worth a lot.

Generative AI and Customer Support
----------------------------------

Yesterday I noted ( https://stratechery.com/2024/nvidia-earnings-inference-=
